üöß **DEVELOPMENT VERSION - NOT FOR PRODUCTION USE** üöß

This is the development version of the Phish Data plugin with experimental features and fixes. Use at your own risk!

Features include comprehensive show information with setlists, community ratings from reviews, venue details, band member profiles, and multi-source image provider for venue and show-specific photos.
